<Class name="CMUI_RTFOutputGenerator" id="906665da-bda1-4ae1-99e0-a120f486a390">
    <superclass name="CMUI_Transient"/>
    <persistentAllowed/>
    <sharedTransientAllowed/>
    <subclassPersistentAllowed/>
    <subclassSharedTransientAllowed/>
    <subclassTransientAllowed/>
    <transientAllowed/>
    <text>Limitations:

1.	Only handles controls which are direct children of the frame
	being printed.
	
2.	Cannot add or move controls during printing.

3.	Only handles HorizontaLine controls which are the entire width
	of the frame being printed.

4.	Does not handle word wrap 

5.	Line height assumed from first control on line

6.	Uses rtf footers but not headers

7.	Handles tables but they must be the only thing on the line.

7.	Assumes A4 paper size.

8.	Does not handle overlapping controls.

9.	Tables suppported but must be the only thing on the line.

10.	Table height assumed to be equal to sum of row heights

11.	Not guaranteed to support programmatic changes to fonts and colours.</text>
    <DbClassMap file="EWSApp"/>
